<p>Is there any way an injectee(EJB, say) know its own injection point?</p>  <pre class="lang-java prettyprint-override"><code>@Stateless public class SomeService {      @PostConstruct     private void constructed() {         // do post construction job         // according to the injectionPoint     }      @Context     private InjectionPoint injectionPoint; // is this possible? } </code></pre>